2020-04-14T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"租借又好，割讓又好，最重要係邊個將主權移交。 1997年英國已將香港主權移交(唔洗話歸還) 俾大陸，咁之前割讓定租借已經唔再重要，因為結果係一樣。<br />\n<br />\n對香港黎講，就算之前英國係租借定擁有香港都好，而加香港主權在大陸，係英國交俾大陸嘅。<br />\n<br />\n台灣方面，如果承認係割讓，咁英國將香港交俾邊個，中華民國都無權過問。如果認為係租借，先可以有d 野講。但即使認為係租借俾英國，咁香港而加響大陸手上，同台灣嘅關係跟大陸其他地方無分別，算係內戰期間失去嘅領土，台灣係有權去討回，大陸唔俾嘅話就只有出兵，台灣加油！<br />\n<br />\n有人話，咁香港人無say 咪好唔公平？ <br />\n<br />\n呢個世界一向都係咁，聯合國將巴勒斯坦一大忽劃俾以色列建國，都無問巴勒斯坦人。<br />\n香港人咪算好彩，對大陸仲有利用價值，否則就好似巴勒斯坦人咁俾猶太人趕出自己屋企，要搭棚訓街，乜都無晒要去求其他國家收留做難民，咁就陰公囉。"},{"pid":"ef3a253c32589b6eca83a2a7dc9a008f57b55d9e","tid":1972251,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"733b90e5a23a36faa977e9f3ec82088bd6db6d75","tid":1972251,"uid":226851,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dccb8bd6e92d9c6aab522b9dabef159919a45b0d","tid":1972251,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/yoshiefans/status/1250026982823231488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyoshiefans%2Fstatus%2F1250026982823231488%3Fs%3D21&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=e38a628a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyoshiefans%2Fstatus%2F1250026982823231488%3Fs%3D21&h=4fe266ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/yoshiefans/status/1250026982823231488?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tvsM7J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tvsM7J.png&h=2d28c505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTweeted <br />\n<br />\n大陸啲歷史書唔知教乜撚<br />\n其實台灣一樣係<span style=\"color: red;\">割讓</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gAOYStMy3PI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgAOYStMy3PI&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=47788ae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gAOYStMy3PI</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1895年馬關條約 永久割讓台灣 澎湖列島</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XBLyLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h